cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting pusch_AntennaPorts to 0 will cause antenna port configuration error and prevent PUSCH transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將 pusch_AntennaPorts 設定為 0 會導致天線埠配置錯誤，並防止 PUSCH 傳輸。
